    <item>
      <title>斯塔默的悲观言论有可能掩盖工党的希望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/starmer-s-doom-and-gloom-risks-eclipsing-labour-message-of-hope</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在议会休会期间，工党高层政客对英国陷入困境的公共财政状况和解决公共财政问题所需采取的严厉措施进行了精心策划的干预，基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 政府的悲观言论也遭到了越来越多的质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/starmer-s-doom-and-gloom-risks-eclipsing-labour-message-of-hope</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾前反对党领袖因腐败指控被捕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/former-taiwan-opposition-leader-held-on-corruption-allegations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾反对党前主席柯文哲因担任台北市长期间发生的房地产开发丑闻，在经过近19个小时的审讯后被逮捕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/former-taiwan-opposition-leader-held-on-corruption-allegations</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 04:07:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美伊拉克部队突袭伊斯兰国武装分子 击毙 15 人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-31/us-iraqi-forces-raid-targeting-islamic-state-group-militants-kills-15-in-western-desert</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迪拜，阿拉伯联合酋长国（美联社）——官员周六称，美国军方和伊拉克在该国西部沙漠针对疑似伊斯兰国组织武装分子发动了联合突袭，造成至少 15 人死亡，七名美军受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-31/us-iraqi-forces-raid-targeting-islamic-state-group-militants-kills-15-in-western-desert</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 01:47:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列扫荡期间西岸汽车袭击致两名袭击者死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/two-assailants-die-in-west-bank-car-attacks-amid-israeli-sweeps</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一辆汽车在约旦河西岸的一个加油站爆炸，另一辆汽车撞入附近的以色列定居点，当局称这是袭击者发动的恐怖袭击，两名袭击者均被击毙。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-31/two-assailants-die-in-west-bank-car-attacks-amid-israeli-sweeps</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 00:29:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党议员对其租住公寓涉嫌“严重缺陷”表示“深切歉意”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-30/mp-profoundly-sorry-for-alleged-pretty-serious-faults-in-flats-he-rents-out</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位新当选的议员表示，对于他所出租的部分公寓存在所谓“相当严重的问题”，他“深感抱歉”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-30/mp-profoundly-sorry-for-alleged-pretty-serious-faults-in-flats-he-rents-out</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 22:37:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普表示最终将投票反对佛罗里达州堕胎法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/trump-says-he-ll-vote-against-florida-abortion-measure-after-all</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普表示，他将投票反对旨在扩大堕胎机会的佛罗里达州修正案，此前这位共和党总统候选人因看似支持该倡议而引起保守派盟友的愤怒。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/trump-says-he-ll-vote-against-florida-abortion-measure-after-all</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 21:57:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普要求无限期推迟其封口费判决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/trump-asks-for-indefinite-delay-for-his-hush-money-sentencing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普请求纽约一名法官无限期推迟对其刑事封口费案的宣判，以便美国法官有时间充分考虑将此案移交联邦法院的请求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/trump-asks-for-indefinite-delay-for-his-hush-money-sentencing</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 20:46:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克挑战最高法院命令 巴西法官禁止 X</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/judge-bans-x-in-brazil-after-musk-refuses-to-name-representative</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于 Facebook 亿万富翁老板埃隆·马斯克拒绝为该社交网络在拉丁美洲最大国家的法定代表人任命，巴西最高法院决定立即暂停 Facebook X 在巴西的服务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/judge-bans-x-in-brazil-after-musk-refuses-to-name-representative</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 19:55:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉声称电网遭到“破坏”，电力供应缓慢恢复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/venezuela-says-sabotage-on-power-grid-led-to-nationwide-outage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗在国家电视台上表示，周五凌晨委内瑞拉全国 24 个州遭遇 12 小时停电，目前该国电力供应正在恢复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/venezuela-says-sabotage-on-power-grid-led-to-nationwide-outage</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 12:07:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克与巴西的冲突加深，威胁 X 和 Starlink</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/starlink-bank-accounts-blocked-in-brazil-to-pay-for-fines-imposed-on-musk-s-x</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克与巴西最高法院一名法官之间的冲突影响到了这位亿万富翁的公司，法官誓言要关闭谷歌 X，并冻结拉丁美洲最大经济体 Starlink 的银行账户。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/starlink-bank-accounts-blocked-in-brazil-to-pay-for-fines-imposed-on-musk-s-x</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 19:45:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
